'''''The Naked Prey'''''<ref>https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/the-naked-prey-1967</ref> ni filime yo muri [[Amerika]] yo mu 1965  yakozwe kandi iyobowe na Cornel Wilde<ref>https://www.britannica.com/topic/The-Naked-Prey</ref>, nawe ukina mu mwanya wa mbere. Bashyizwe muri veldt yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo, imigambi ya firime yibanda kumuyobozi wa safari ugerageza kubaho mubuzima bubi bwa veldt<ref>http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title/4727/the-naked-prey/</ref>, mugihe agerageza kwirinda urupfu rwatewe nabarwanyi ba [[Afurika|Afrika]] bihorera<ref>http://www.tcm.com/video/1378316/naked-prey-the-1966-original-trailer/</ref>. Iyinkuru ishingiye kuburambe bw'umushakashatsi [[Amerika|w'umunyamerika]] John Colter<ref>https://www.criterion.com/films/848-the-naked-prey</ref> . Amashusho yamamaye yinjije abanditsi Clint Johnson na Don Peters mu gihembo cya Akademiki cyiza cyumwimerere <ref>https://www.nytimes.com/1966/06/15/archives/screen-the-naked-preycornel-wilde-is-chased-through-the-jungles.html</ref>.

Iyi filime yerekanwe bwa mbere mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya San Sebastián 1965, nyuma isohoka muri [[Amerika]] ku ya 23 Werurwe 1966<ref>https://www.tvguide.com/movies/the-naked-prey/review/2000114583/</ref>. Iyi filime yakozwe ku ngengo yimari itarenga 700.000 $, iyi firime yafatiwe ahantu hose muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo<ref>https://eurekavideo.co.uk/movie/the-naked-prey/</ref>.

== uko yakozwe ==
''The Naked Prey yafatiwe'' amashusho muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo.    Amashusho ya firime yari afite impapuro icyenda gusa.   Amazina yatangije iyi filime yaherekejwe n’ibishushanyo byerekanwe n’umuhanzi waho Andrew Motjuoadi<ref>https://filmclassics.com.au/product/the-naked-prey-cornel-wilde-new-dvd/</ref>.

